*:Zone.Identifier

# Claude hook temporary files (session-specific ephemeral state)
# Note: For this SOURCE project, we ignore the entire .sidekick/ directory
# since it only contains test/development runtime data.
# Consumer projects should use these patterns in their .gitignore:
#   .sidekick/*.log
#   .sidekick/sessions/
# to track .sidekick/sidekick.conf and .sidekick/README.md
.claude/hooks/sidekick
.sidekick/
*.backup.*
*.uninstall-backup.*

# DevContainer environment variables (contains secrets)
.devcontainer/.env

